title: 16 Times Kim Kardashian Almost Passed for a Regular Mom
text:
16 Times Kim Kardashian Almost Passed for a Regular Mom Meredith Gordon 
Splash News Her life is one celeb filled red carpet after another, but at heart, Kim Kardashian is not all that different from any other mom. She's just a busy parent trying to find enough time in her day to do all the things she needs to do. 
Even though Kim may go to North's dance class wearing sky high heels, and she may push a stroller wearing a vault worth of couture, she's pretty much a normal mom at heart. And once in a while, she comes fairly close to blending in with the rest of the mom crowd. Well, almost . Here are all the times Kim came "this" close to being just like the rest of us.
